+# SPRINT: Deterministically Bound Critic + Founder Canary
+
+Objective: replace model-echoed provenance with deterministic binding (CRITIC_SYSTEM_V3), correct the
+semantic oracle (corpus-v2, no goal confound), calibrate Flash-Lite vs Haiku (≤4 paid), and — only if one
+qualifies — make the grounded V2 plan selectable via the real entrypoint for an allowlisted founder canary
+(≤2 paid). Max 6 cumulative paid calls in ONE append-only ledger.
+
+## Hard rules
+- LLM proposes; deterministic disposes. Strict parse reject-never-repair. Model NEVER authors provenance ids.
+- No model computes budget/payout. Exact base-unit budget equality mandatory. Default off.
+- No deploy/push/migration/funding/launch/payout/global-model-approval.
+- Do NOT modify: payout, Concierge, browser security, evidence renderer, architect DRAFT COMPILER.
+- Candidates ONLY: google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview, anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5. No Pro/Sonnet/Opus/search.
+
+## Phase progress (update as I go — NO speculative results)
+- [x] P0 — append-only v1 amendment. COMMIT 7da0713.
+- [x] P1 — CRITIC_SYSTEM_V3 + CRITIC_TRANSPORT_SCHEMA_V3 + CriticV3Schema + decisionId binding in the shadow.
+      V2 constant + transport kept for history; V2 Zod removed. Entrypoint tests → V3 (25 pass). COMMIT.
+- [x] P2 — corpus-v2 + scorer-v2 + tests (8). COMMIT.
+- [x] P3 — deterministic proof tests (5). COMMIT.
+- [x] P4 — 2-model blind calibration. COMMIT c3b1201. WINNER = google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview
+      (grounding_critic_canary_candidate). Haiku ineligible (rep1 llm_strict_not_object, no rep2). 3 paid calls.
+      Evidence: promotion-evidence/grounding-critic-semantic-v2{.json,.ledger.json}. A CRITIC IS ELIGIBLE →
+      Phases 5+6 PROCEED. Caveat: candidate_a consistent=false (verdict granularity varied 1 case; paySafe 1.0 both).
+- [x] P5 — canary mode + mission-canary.ts (authority + strict gate + digest + approval) + pipeline/job wiring.
+      COMMIT 2e62ece. 26 deterministic tests; full suite 1385 green. No migration. Default off. Shadow unchanged.
+- [x] P6 — canary smoke run. COMMIT 50437d2. 2 paid calls (flash-lite architect+critic). Model stages ALL passed
+      live (architect ok → draft compiled → action_replayed → V3 criticSupported=1); blocked at canonical gate
+      due to a HARNESS empty-scope defect (not model/product). Not re-run (cap). Selection tail proven zero-paid
+      by the new deterministic "selection completes end-to-end" test. Amendment records the honest read.
+- [ ] FINAL — patch + manifest + report (14 items). Regenerate export fresh (ignore stale sage-*.patch in tree).
+
+## Paid-call ledger tally (cap 6) — record BEFORE each dispatch
+- P4 calibration: 3 used (2× candidate_a ok, 1× candidate_b failed-transport).
+- P6 canary smoke: 2 used (architect + V3 critic, both flash-lite).
+- TOTAL: 5 / 6.
+
+## Key facts / decisions
+- V2 critic constant CRITIC_SYSTEM_V2 / CRITIC_TRANSPORT_SCHEMA stays exported for the historical corpus-v1
+  bakeoff test (grounding-critic-bakeoff.live.test.ts) — DO NOT modify that file.
+- Shadow moves to V3 (decisionId). Entrypoint test critic fixtures update to {verdicts:[{decisionId,verdict}]}.
+- Ledger for P4: promotion-evidence/grounding-critic-semantic-v2.ledger.json (calibration + canary share cap 6).
